Detailed Description

This structure defines the parameters needed for configuring a particular AMMU page.

Field Documentation

AMMU Page Number. Number of pages present in hardware differs for different page types

AMMU Page Type. Refer enum ammuPageType_t for values

Physical Address that is mapped to logical address
